 * ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
 * ║  [B2B] Snippet 13: GitHub Webhook Sync                       ║
 * ║  Version: V.22.0 — Fix merge commit sync + Compare API fallback ║
 * ║  DINOCO B2B Smart Order System                               ║
 * ╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
 * ║  Push to GitHub → Webhook → WordPress REST API               ║
 * ║  → อัพเดท code ใน wp_snippets table อัตโนมัติ                  ║
 * ╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
 * ║  Required constants in wp-config.php:                        ║
 * ║    B2B_GITHUB_WEBHOOK_SECRET  — shared secret                ║
 * ║    B2B_GITHUB_TOKEN           — personal access token        ║
 * ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
 *
 * V.22.0 Changes:
 * - Fix: Merge commits (PR merge) have empty modified/added arrays in webhook payload
 *   → Detect merge commits by message pattern "Merge pull request" or "Merge branch"
 *   → Force full sync for merge commits (all 13 snippets, ~2s overhead)
 *   → No more "no_snippet_files_changed" false negatives on PR merge
 * - Fix: Compare API fallback could fail silently (timeout, rate limit)
 *   → Add logging for Compare API failures
 *   → Fallback to full sync if Compare API fails (instead of skipping)
 *
 * V.19.0 Changes:
 * - Fix: wpdb->update() writes to DB but object cache serves stale snippet code
 *   → New helper: b2b_sync_update_snippet() with return value check
 *   → wp_cache_flush() after every DB write
 *   → Delete Code Snippets transients + WP Fastest Cache clear
 *   → Verify-after-write: read back + compare MD5 hash
 *   → Applied to both webhook sync AND manual sync paths
 *
 * V.18.0 Changes:
 * - Add: [b2b_sync_dashboard] shortcode — Admin debug dashboard
 *   → ดูสถานะ sync, config check, snippet table, manual sync button
 *   → ใส่ shortcode ในหน้า WP page → เปิดด้วย admin ได้เลย
 *
 * V.17.0 Changes:
 * - Fix: raw.githubusercontent.com CDN cache serving stale content
 *   → ใช้ commit SHA (data['after']) แทน branch name ใน raw URL
 *   → Commit SHA URL ไม่มี cache เพราะ immutable
 *   → Fallback Contents API ก็ใช้ commit SHA เช่นกัน
 *
 * V.16.1 Changes:
 * - Fix: html_entity_decode() on DB snippet names before GitHub URL construction
 *   → Recreated snippets stored &amp; instead of & → 404 on raw download
 *   → Affects snippets with & or special chars in name (S1, S2, etc.)
 *
 * V.16.0 Changes:
 * - Fix: api.github.com timeout (cURL error 28) จาก WP hosting
 *   → ใช้ raw.githubusercontent.com แทน API (เร็วกว่า + reliable กว่า)
 *   → ตัด directory listing ออก — ใช้ commit data + DB mapping แทน
 * - Fix: duplicate DB rows ชน regex (1A/1B/1C/1D)
 *   → regex (?![A-Za-z]) + active=1 filter + first-match wins
 *
 * V.15.0: shutdown hook + fastcgi_finish_request() (WP-Cron unreliable)
 *         + execution lock + refactor b2b_do_full_sync()
 *
 * V.5.0: Contents API (fix private repo download)
